<title>DRIFTING DOWN</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1. Na kuong tawl phatloh ziekin,
 Kuong chawlhna mun nuom apat,
 Tuilien in awl awlin a hun tawk zel hi;
 A thukna lai lam zuonin,
 Tuipi lien leh lauhum ah,
 Tuilien in awl awl in a hun tawk zel hi.

[V2]
 A hun tawk gamla deuh deuh hi,
 Tuipi lien leh lauhum ah;
 Pathien lungsietna, bitna huongsung apatin,
 Manthaina mun lam zuonin,
 Tuilien in awl awlin ahun tawk zel hi.

[V3]
 2. Gam nuom lama thilvak chun,
 Um ding dan a hun hilh zing,
 Tuilien in awl awlin a huntawk zel hi;
 Kuongchawlhna mun apatin,
 Na kuong tawk mang pai khana,
 Tuilien in awl awl in a hun tawk zel hi.

[V4]
 3. Gam nuom apata Aw chun,
 A hun sapnau chuh ngaiin,
 Tuilien in awl awl in a hun tawk zel hi;
 Khai, suohpih, a Awu ngaiin,
 A phat a kikhelh mahin,
 Tuilien in awl awl in a hun tawk zel hi.</lyrics>
</song>